divs: sighting details i was taking pics of the "pink moon" on 4\17\11. i was using a kodak 10.2 mega pixel camara affixed to a tripod. lens setting was for distant scenery at night. pics were taken from an upstairs bedroom with no glass or screens in place. no inside lights were on & no flash was used. i took about 12 pics but only 1 showed anything. i downloaded them the next day but didn't immeadiatly notice anything. this object was the only 1 out of about 1200 pics i have taken with this camera. what ever this is in the picture is partially behind a prominant tree in the shot so this couldn't be a reflection. respectfully hedlok
Summary: Unknown object in night time photo
